  "description": "<p>上周在休士顿召开的全球合作伙伴大会上鲍尔默在开幕式上表示：“我们的数据中心基础设施中服务器的数量已经超过了100万台。”对此前微软团队成员，现亚 马逊副总裁 James Hamilton<strong>在私人博客中预估微软使用的服务器每台的功率在150W到300W之间，这就意味着所有服务器的功率在3亿瓦左右。如果这些数据正确的话 那么就意味着每年微软单单花费在服务器电力消耗上就达到了2,629,743 MWh或者每小时2.6terawatt，相当于能够为美国23000户家庭供电。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ee9785a/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245359.htm&amp;t=%E6%9D%A5%E7%AE%97%E7%AE%97%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF100%E4%B8%87%E5%8F%B0%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%80%BB%E8%8A%B1%E8%B4%B9%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245359.htm&amp;t=%E6%9D%A5%E7%AE%97%E7%AE%97%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF100%E4%B8%87%E5%8F%B0%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%80%BB%E8%8A%B1%E8%B4%B9%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245359.htm&amp;t=%E6%9D%A5%E7%AE%97%E7%AE%97%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF100%E4%B8%87%E5%8F%B0%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%80%BB%E8%8A%B1%E8%B4%B9%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245359.htm&amp;t=%E6%9D%A5%E7%AE%97%E7%AE%97%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF100%E4%B8%87%E5%8F%B0%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%80%BB%E8%8A%B1%E8%B4%B9%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feed