  "description": "<p>被很多人视为现实版“钢铁侠”埃伦·马斯克（Elon Musk）早已功成名就，他参与创建的在线支付平台Paypal、电动汽车公司特斯拉和太空技术公司SpaceX目前都运营良好。<strong>但是，这位永不满足的科 技狂人最近又有惊人举动——他提出的最新交通项目“Hyperloop”志在让从洛杉矶到旧金山的时间缩短至半小时内。这个Hyperloop到底是什 么？科技博客网站The Verge日前对它可能涉及的原理和问题做了介绍。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ee97859/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245360.htm&amp;t=%E7%9C%8B%E9%A9%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B%E2%80%9C%E8%B6%85%E7%BA%A7%E9%AB%98%E9%93%81%E2%80%9D%E6%98%AF%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%BF%90%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245360.htm&amp;t=%E7%9C%8B%E9%A9%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B%E2%80%9C%E8%B6%85%E7%BA%A7%E9%AB%98%E9%93%81%E2%80%9D%E6%98%AF%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%BF%90%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245360.htm&amp;t=%E7%9C%8B%E9%A9%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B%E2%80%9C%E8%B6%85%E7%BA%A7%E9%AB%98%E9%93%81%E2%80%9D%E6%98%AF%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%BF%90%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245360.htm&amp;t=%E7%9C%8B%E9%A9%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B%E2%80%9C%E8%B6%85%E7%BA%A7%E9%AB%98%E9%93%81%E2%80%9D%E6%98%AF%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%BF%90%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245360.